text:
>log.c:330: conflicting types for `ap_open_logs'
>/usr/local/include/http_log.h:154: previous declaration of `ap_open_logs'

You've got include files from a previous install of Apache (apache 1.3 perhaps?)
in /usr/local/include.  Get the old Apache headers out of /usr/local/include and
you'll be happy.

creator: jorton@redhat.com
